# Customer

Customer adds product to the shopping cart

## Create Order [/createOrder]

### Customer adds products to shopping cart [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "text": "Please Enter the following: ",
            "fields": [
                "Product ID": "PXXX-XXXXX",
                "Deal ID": "DXXX-XXXXX",
                "Quantity": 0001"
            ]
        }


+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
              "message":"Your order has been saved successfully."
            }
        ]


## View Profile [/viewProfile]

### Customer views his profile [GET]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "userId": "12345"
        }


+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
               {
                "userId": "12345",
                "firstName": "John",
                "lastName": "Doe",
                 "email": "johndoe@example.com",
                 "phone": "+1234567890",
                "address": "123 Main St, Anytown USA"
}
        ]


## Update Profile [/updateProfile]

### Customer updates their profile [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

{
  "userId": "12345",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "johndoe@example.com",
  "phone": "+1234567890",
  "address": "123 Main St, Anytown USA"
}



+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
{
  "success": true,
  "message": 'User $['userId] details updated successfully.'
}

        ]

