# Vendor Admin

Deals by Vendors        
        
## Create Deals [/createDeals]

### Vendor creates the deal [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "fields":  [
                "vendorId": "12345", // already filled,
                "productId": , //dropdown choices
                "dealName": "Special Offer",
                "description": "Get 20% off on all orders over $50",
                "startDate": "2023-03-01", // date field
                "endDate": "2023-03-31" // date field
            ]    
        }


+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
              "message":"Your deal created successfully."
            }
        ]
        

## Delete Deals [/deleteDeals]

### Vendor deletes deals [DELETE]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
        
            "Deal ID": "VXXXX", 
            
        }


+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {   
              "Deal ID": "VXXXX",
              "message":"Deal has been created successfully."
            }
        ]
               
        
# Super Admin

Super Admin creates the vendor

## Create Vendor [/createVendor]

### Super Admin creates vendor[POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "text": "Please Enter the following: ",
            "fields": [
                "Vendor ID": "VXXXX", //default
                "Vendor Name": "Vendor Name",
                "Description": "Lorem Ipsum"
            ]
        }


+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
              "message":"Vendor has been created successfully."
            }
        ]
        
        
## Delete Vendor [/deleteVendor]

### Super Admin deletes vendor [DELETE]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
        
            "Vendor ID": "VXXXX", 
            
        }


+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {   
              "Vendor ID": "VXXXX",
              "message":"Vendor has been created successfully."
            }
        ]
        
        
